    title="Discover more about WunderCove and its Journey"
    information={`Our blog dives deeper into the story behind each WunderCove. 
                 Learn about the farmers we partner with, the care that goes into every product, 
                 and the importance of choosing high-quality, sustainable food. 
                 Stay connected with new updates, seasonal box releases, and ways you can support local agriculture 
                 while enjoying the finest European imports.`}
  />

